<h1>Configure Your StreamDeck Timer</h1>

<div class="setup-steps">
  <h3>Step 1: Configure StreamDeck Button</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Open StreamDeck software</li>
    <li>Drag a "Website" action to your desired button</li>
    <li>In URL field enter: <code>http://0.0.0.0:9987/timer?time=300&topic=Break_Time</code></li>
    <li>Adjust time (in seconds) and topic as needed</li>
  </ol>

  <h3>Step 2: Set Button Image</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>Download this image for your button:</li>
    <li><img src="/streamdeck-beaver-key-black.png" alt="StreamDeck Key" class="key-image"></li>
    <li>In StreamDeck software, click the button image field</li>
    <li>Upload the downloaded beaver image</li>
  </ol>
</div>

<h3>Example URLs</h3>
<ul>
  <li>5 minute break: <code>http://0.0.0.0:9987/timer?time=300&topic=Break_Time</code></li>
  <li>25 minute focus: <code>http://0.0.0.0:9987/timer?time=1500&topic=Focus_Session</code></li>
</ul>
